{"tid":1861990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請其他工會助攻 (罷工)","createTime":"2020-02-04T11:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:26:38.000Z","uid":270181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3827fafae449c486fa61a0fb70f76128b412ab","tid":1861990,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"醫護界會在社區爆發復工，政府就唔會理你。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋會心諗，反正都會復工，使鬼理你！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以請其他工會為醫護界助攻</span></span><br />\n<br />\n罷工，向政府施更大壓。<br />\n（雖然對政府都無咩希望）<br />\n<br />\n要做就快，無咩時間，要同個菌鬥快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人救香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1655c8251f28a6431336d9f22d7abb7fd486bae","tid":1861990,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:42:11.000Z","msg":"終於有人話"},{"pid":"8a0c25d7bec38990f0ae2342eea2bc11571f7bad","tid":1861990,"uid":270181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"求幫推，醫護界捱唔到好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed1ba0d973a8ef8e527fc998f44fa6f0595baf6","tid":1861990,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHgdShX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHgdShX.jpg&h=ce6f5cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">組織工會<br />\n有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］<br />\n香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝"},{"pid":"120a154bfd6da742bd0c54527eff1a7525cd3356","tid":1861990,"uid"